OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776753489
OL,3,CReport reveals business plans for
OL,4,CBrighton i360 suffered from 'optimism
OL,5,Cbias'
OL,7,FA report identifying that business
OL,8,Fplans for the Brighton i360 suffered
OL,9,Ffrom "optimism bias", will be
OL,10,Fdiscussed at a council meeting on
OL,11,FTuesday (21 April).
OL,13,FThe attraction closed unexpectedly in
OL,14,F2024 shortly after entering
OL,15,Fadministration.
OL,17,FIt later reopened under new ownership,
OL,18,Fafter the local authority wrote off
OL,19,F#51 million owed by the attraction.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
