FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776753489
OL,3,CReport reveals business plans for
OL,4,CBrighton i360 suffered from 'optimism
OL,5,Cbias'
OL,7,FThe council says it will now
OL,8,F"carefully consider" the findings of
OL,9,Fthe report published last month, into
OL,10,Fit's future decision making processes.
OL,12,FIt said the report makes a number of
OL,13,Frecommendations to "help reduce
OL,14,Fsimilar risks in the future".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776753489
OL,3,CReport reveals business plans for
OL,4,CBrighton i360 suffered from 'optimism
OL,5,Cbias'
OL,7,FThat includes what it said is "the
OL,8,Fneed for more robust and realistic
OL,9,Ffinancial modelling, improved
OL,10,Fbenchmarking against comparable local
OL,11,Fmarkets, independent market validation
OL,12,Fand clearer governance and assurance
OL,13,Farrangements".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776753489
OL,3,CReport reveals business plans for
OL,4,CBrighton i360 suffered from 'optimism
OL,5,Cbias'
OL,7,FCouncillor Jacob Taylor, Deputy Leader
OL,8,Fand Cabinet member for Finance and
OL,9,FCity Regeneration, said: "We're really
OL,10,Fpleased to see the Brighton i360 doing
OL,11,Fwell over the past year under
OL,12,FNightcap's ownership, helping to draw
OL,13,Fresidents and visitors to that part of
OL,14,Fthe seafront.
OL,16,F"This marks a new chapter for the
OL,17,Fattraction, and it's in everyone's
OL,18,Finterests for it to succeed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776753489
OL,3,CReport reveals business plans for
OL,4,CBrighton i360 suffered from 'optimism
OL,5,Cbias'
OL,7,F"The council's original investment
OL,8,Fcame at considerable cost to the
OL,9,Fpublic, which is why we commissioned
OL,10,Fthis independent report to ensure
OL,11,Fmistake of this scale is not repeated.
OL,13,F"While it looks back at decisions made
OL,14,Fat the time, what's most important is
OL,15,Fthat we learn from it and use those
OL,16,Flessons to inform future commercial
OL,17,Fand investment decisions involving
OL,18,Fpublic money."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
